 low sodium''\n\t|<ref>{{cite web | url = https://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/vegetables-and-vegetable-products/7666/2 | title = Sauerkraut, canned, low sodium Nutrition Facts & Calories | access-date = 2019-02-15 | publisher = Self Nutrition Data, Cond\u00e9 Nast | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180625113212/http://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/vegetables-and-vegetable-products/7666/2 | archivedate = 2018-06-25 }}</ref>\n\t|100\n\t|26\n\t|25\n\t|1 : 1\n|-\n|''[[Spinach]], cooked, boiled, drained, without salt''\n\t|<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/vegetables-and-vegetable-products/2627/2 | title = Spinach, cooked, boiled, drained, without salt Nutrition Facts & Calories | language = en-US | access-date = 2019-02-17 | publisher = Self Nutrition Data, Cond\u00e9 Nast | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190104104129/https://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/vegetables-and-vegetable-products/2627/2 | archivedate = 2019-01-04 }}</ref>\n\t|100\n\t|17\n\t|92\n\t|1 : 5.4\n|-\n|''[[Turnip greens]], cooked''\n\t|<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/vegetables-and-vegetable-products/2704/2 | title =  Turnip greens, cooked, boiled, drained, without salt Nutrition Facts & Calories | language = en-US | access-date = 2019-02-17 | publisher = Self Nutrition Data, Cond\u00e9 Nast | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190105172712/https://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/vegetables-and-vegetable-products/2704/2 | archivedate = 2019-01-05 }}</ref>\n\t|100\n\t|28\n\t|64\n\t|1 : 2.3\n|-\n|''[[Dandelion greens]], cooked''\n|{{Citation needed | date = February 2019}}\n|1/2 cup\n| -\n|0.1\n| -\n|-\n|''[[Kale]], cooked''\n|{{Citation needed | date = February 2019}}\n|1/2 cup\n|0.1\n|0.1\n|1 : 1\n|-\n|''[[Kohlrabi]] raw''\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/vegetables-and-vegetable-products/2466/2|title=Kohlrabi, raw}}</ref>\n|1 cup\n|27\n|35\n|1 : 1.7\n|-\n|''[[Beet greens]], cooked''\n\t|<ref>{{Cit